OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPrison living costs        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fscrapped for wrongly       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fconvicted                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A controversial rule which deducted    
OL,6, living costs from compensation paid to 
OL,7, wrongly jailed people has been         
OL,8, scrapped.                              
OL,10,FThe government rethink follows the case
OL,11,Fof Andrew Malkinson, who spent 17 years
OL,12,Fin jail for a rape he did not commit.  
OL,14,FHe welcomed the move but said he still 
OL,15,Ffaces a two-year wait for his payment. 
OL,17,FSpeaking to the BBC, Mr Malkinson said:
OL,18,F"It's a step in the right direction.   
OL,19,FBut there's much more that needs       
OL,20,Fchanging too.                          
